    "code": "#include <stdio.h>\n\nint main() {\n    int num = 10;\n    float f = 3.14;\n    double d = 3.14159;\n    char c = 'A';\n    int arr[3] = {1, 2, 3};\n\n    printf(\"arr[0] = %d\\n\", arr[0]);\n    printf(\"Size of double: %lu bytes\\n\", sizeof(d));\n    return 0;\n}"
